data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and 2 car garage with bonus area upstairs that could be converted to extra living space. This home is on a wooded lot in the desirable Argyll Subdivision. Enter the home into a large foyer with entrance to living room and bonus room/office space. Beautiful kitchen with double oven. Upstairs is a large primary bedroom, 3 bedrooms, and a bathroom. There is an abundance of closets and storage space in this home. Sunroom to enjoy the views of all the seasons. Don't miss out on this one. Call today for your private showing.
